                                            Verification Code
                                        </p>
                                        <p style="margin:0 0 0 0;font-size:26px;line-height:24px;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight: 500;color: #302D86;letter-spacing: 30px;">
                                            @Model.OTPNumber
